                            [color=#ffda75]Dark Knight[/color]
                        [/td]
                        [td style="text-align:left; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle;"]• Souleater, Last Resort for DPS  
