        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color:#E0E0E0;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-enmity-types style="
                font-size:20px; 
                color: #cea425; 
                text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]Enmity Types & Characteristics
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
                [/div]

                [table style="border:3px ridge #b08d57; box-shadow: inset 0 0 6px #5b4b2d;"]
                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                    [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; width:33.33%; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Enmity Type[/th]
                    [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; width:33.33%; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Maximum[/th]
                    [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; width:33.33%; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Details[/th]
                    [/tr]

                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                    [td style="color:#ffa07a; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Volatile Enmity (VE)[/td]
                    [td style="color:#ffa07a; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]30,000[/td]
                    [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]• Decay Rate: [color=#ffa07a]-60 VE/sec[/color][/td]
                    [/tr]

                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                    [td style="color:#ffa366; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Cumulative Enmity (CE)[/td]
                    [td style="color:#ffa366; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]30,000[/td]
                    [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]• Formula: ([color=#ffa366]CE[/color] × [color=#d64848]Damage[/color]) ÷ [color=#7fe07f]Max HP[/color][/td]
                    [/tr]

                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                    [td style="color:#ff4500; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Total Enmity (TE)[/td]
                    [td style="color:#ff4500; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]60,000[/td]
                    [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]• Targeting priority = [color=#ffa07a]VE[/color] + [color=#ffa366]CE[/color][/td]
                    [/tr]
                [/table][/div]
        [/div]
        

        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color:#E0E0E0;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-optimize-ce style="
                font-size:20px; 
                color: #cea425; 
                text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]Optimizing CE loss Reduction with Gear and Enmity+
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
                [/div]

                [div style="text-align:left"][color=#cea425][b]Managing Cumulative Enmity (CE) is vital, especially in multi-target fights. Reduce CE loss via:[/b][/color]
                    • Enmity+ stats  
                    • Gear with “Reduces Enmity Loss”  
                    • The bard song Foe Sirvente  

                    These stack multiplicatively, allowing up to 75% CE loss reduction.

                    [color=#cea425][b]Example:[/b][/color]
                    With +100 Enmity gear (50% reduction) plus Foe Sirvente (50%):  
                    Total = 1 - [(1 - 0.50) × (1 - 0.50)] = 75%  
                    You lose only 25% CE when taking damage.

                    [color=#cea425][b]Tips:[/b][/color]
                    • Prioritize survivability (DT, PDT, MDT).  
                    • Use Foe Sirvente in multi-enemy fights.  
                    • Avoid overcapping CE reduction by balancing gear.

                    [div align="center"][table style="border:3px ridge #b08d57; box-shadow: inset 0 0 6px #5b4b2d;"]
                            [tr style="background: linear-gradient(to top, #b08d57, #806a38); box-shadow: inset 0 -3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);"]
                [th colspan="7" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:bold; color:#332b05; text-shadow:0 0 1px #806a35, 0px 0px 2px #b7974d;"]Types of CE Loss Reduction[/th]
                            [/tr]
                            [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                                [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Source[/th]
                                [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Max Contribution[/th]
                                [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Notes[/th]
                            [/tr]

                            [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                                [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"][color=#ff7f50]Enmity+[/color][/td]
                                [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"][color=#ff7f50]50%[/color][/td]
                                [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:left; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]1% reduction per +2 Enmity, capped at +100 Enmity.[/td]
                            [/tr]

                            [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                                [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"][color=#ffb380]Reduced Enmity Loss (Gear + Foe Sirvente)[/color][/td]
                                [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"][color=#ffa366]50%[/color][/td]
                                [td style="color:#E0E0E0; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle; text-align:left; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"][div style="padding:3px"][url=http://www.ffxiah.com/item/20687/burtgang target="\_blank"][img]https://static.ffxiah.com/images/icon/20687.png[/img][/url] [color=#F7D58B]Burtgang[/color] ([color=#ffa366]-20%[/color])[/div]
                                    [div style="padding:3px"][url=http://www.ffxiah.com/item/23627/chevaliers-cuisses-1 target="\_blank"][img]https://static.ffxiah.com/images/icon/23627.png[/img][/url] [color=#F7D58B]Chevalier's Cuisses +3[/color] ([color=#ffa366]-14%[/color])[/div]
                                    [div style="padding:3px"][url=https://www.ffxiah.com/item/11595/creed-collar target="\_blank"][img]https://static.ffxiah.com/images/icon/11595.png[/img][/url] [color=#F7D58B]Creed Collar[/color] ([color=#ffa366]-5%[/color])[/div]
                                    [div style="padding:3px"][url=https://www.bg-wiki.com/ffxi/Foe_Sirvente target="\_blank"][img]https://www.bg-wiki.com/images/1/17/Foe_Sirvente_%28Scroll%29_icon.png[/img][/url] [color=#00ffd0]Foe Sirvente[/color]: Adds up to [color=#ffa366]50%[/color] reduction, combined with gear effects. Shares the same cap as gear effects.[/div]
                                [/td]
                            [/tr]

                            [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                                [td colspan="3" style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; vertical-align:middle;"]Maximum Total Reduction: [color=#ffa366]75%[/color]  
                                    This is achieved through [color=#f27126]50% Enmity+[/color] and 50% Gear/Foe Sirvente, applied multiplicatively:  
                                    [color=#ffa366]Total Reduction[/color] = 1 - [(1 - 0.50) × (1 - 0.50)] = [color=#ffa366]75%[/color].
                                [/td]
                            [/tr]
                        [/table][/div][/div]
            [/div]
        [/div]
        

        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color:#E0E0E0;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-enmity-healing style="
                font-size:20px; 
                color: #cea425; 
                text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]Enmity Generated by Healing
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
                [/div]

                [div align="left"][table width="1000px" style="border:none;"]
                        [tr]
                            [td width="250px" style="vertical-align:top; border:none;"]
                                [color=#cea425][b]Simplified Enmity Calculations:[/b][/color]
                                Cumulative Enmity (CE):
                                • CE = (HP Healed × 0.231)  
                                • Divided by the number of enemies (min CE = 1)
                                Volatile Enmity (VE):
                                • VE = CE × 6

                                [color=#cea425][b]Key Points:[/b][/color]
                                • Enmity+ increases CE & VE  
                                • Enmity- can reduce CE to 1

                                [color=#cea425][b]Example:[/b][/color]
                                • Self-healing set: Enmity+87  
                                • Final CE = ((Base CE ÷ mob count) × (1 + Enmity+/100))  
                                • Final VE = Final CE × 6
                            [/td]

                            [td width="200px" style="vertical-align:middle; border:none;"][div align="left"][table width="600px" style="border:3px ridge #b08d57; box-shadow: inset 0 0 6px #5b4b2d;"][tr style="background: linear-gradient(to top, #b08d57, #806a38); box-shadow: inset 0 -3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);"]
                                            [th colspan="7" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:bold; color:#332b05; text-shadow:0 0 1px #806a35, 0px 0px 2px #b7974d;"]Enmity Generation (1 Mob)[/th]
                                        [/tr]
                                        [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
