        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color:#E0E0E0;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-enmity-atonement style="
                font-size:20px; 
                color: #cea425; 
                text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]Atonement Mechanics
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
                [/div]

                [div align="left"]
                    [table width="1000px" style="border:none;"]
                        [tr]
                            [td width="250px" style="vertical-align:top; border:none;"]
                                [color=#cea425][b]Enmity Damage Formula Explained:[/b][/color]
                                • ((CE ÷ 6) - 1) + ((VE ÷ 6) - 1)

                                [color=#cea425][b]Key Mechanics:[/b][/color]
                                • The Enmity multiplier (fTP mod) is capped at x3 when reaching 3000 TP.  
                                • Additional TP bonuses (like gorgets or belts) do not increase the cap beyond x3.

                                [color=#cea425][b]Gear Bonuses:[/b][/color]
                                • Certain gear, such as R15 Burtgang, enhances the multiplier, but cannot exceed x3.

                                [color=#cea425][b]Important Notes and Tips:[/b][/color]
                                • Maximize your CE and VE for higher enmity-based damage.  
                                • Focus on Enmity+ gear and multipliers to optimize efficiency.  
                                • The hard cap of x3 cannot be bypassed regardless of gear.
                            [/td]

                            [td width="300px" style="vertical-align:middle; border:none;"]
                                [table width="300px" style="border:3px ridge #b08d57; box-shadow: inset 0 0 6px #5b4b2d;"]
                                    [tr style="background: linear-gradient(to top, #b08d57, #806a38); box-shadow: inset 0 -3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);"]
                                        [th colspan="7" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:bold; color:#332b05; text-shadow:0 0 1px #806a35, 0px 0px 2px #b7974d;"]Atonement Enmity (Burtgang)[/th]
                                    [/tr]
                                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Category[/th]
                                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-right:1px solid #707070;"]CE[/th]
                                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-right:1px solid #707070;"]VE[/th]
                                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);"]Total[/th]
                                    [/tr]
                                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                                        [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"][color=#F7D58B]Base Generation[/color][/td]
                                        [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"][color=#ff9966]300[/color][/td]
                                        [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"][color=#ff7f50]900[/color][/td]
                                        [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070;"][color=#ff7f50]1200[/color][/td]
                                    [/tr]
