        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color:#E0E0E0;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-enmity-generation style="
                font-size:20px; 
                color: #cea425; 
                text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]Enmity Generation
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
                [/div]

                [div align="left"][color=#cea425][b]Understanding Enmity Generation:[/b][/color]  
                    Enmity generation in combat is influenced by two main factors: the Base Value of an action and the Total Modifier applied through gear and buffs. Balancing these factors is essential for managing threat and maintaining control in battle.

                    [color=#cea425][b]Formula Overview:[/b][/color]  
                    • Base Value: Defined by the action, divided into Volatile Enmity (VE) and Cumulative Enmity (CE).  
                    • Final Enmity = Base Enmity × Total Modifier  
                    • Total Modifier: Derived from:  
                    • Equipment Bonus: Enmity gained from gear (e.g., +159% with the Full Enmity Set).  
                    • Crusade Buff: Additional +30% enmity from the Crusade spell.  

                    [color=#cea425][b]Example Calculation:[/b][/color]  
                    An action with 1,000 VE using the Full Enmity Set (+159%) and Crusade (+30%):  
                    1,000 VE × (1 + 1.59 + 0.30) = 2,890 VE.
                [/div]

                [table style="border:3px ridge #b08d57; box-shadow: inset 0 0 6px #5b4b2d;"]
                    [tr style="background: linear-gradient(to top, #b08d57, #806a38); box-shadow: inset 0 -3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);"]
                        [th colspan="7" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:bold; color:#332b05; text-shadow:0 0 1px #806a35, 0px 0px 2px #b7974d;"]Enmity Gear Sets[/th]
                    [/tr]
                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Equipment Set[/th]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Equipment Bonus[/th]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Crusade Bonus[/th]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Total Modifier[/th]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Optimal Use[/th]
                    [/tr]
                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                        [td style="color:#F7D58B; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Full Enmity Set[/td]
                        [td style="color:#66ccff; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]+159%[/td]
                        [td style="color:#00ffd0; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]+30%[/td]
                        [td style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]×2.89[/td]
                        [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Maximize enmity with [color=#00ffd0]Flash[/color], [color=#00ffd0]Jettatura[/color], [color=#e5d522]Provoke[/color][/td]
                    [/tr]
                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                        [td style="color:#F7D58B; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]SIRD Enmity Set[/td]
                        [td style="color:#66ccff; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]+114%[/td]
                        [td style="color:#00ffd0; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]+30%[/td]
                        [td style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]×2.44[/td]
                        [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Balanced enmity and [color=#F7D58B]SIRD[/color] for spellcasting[/td]
                    [/tr]
                [/table]
                [table style="border:3px ridge #b08d57; box-shadow: inset 0 0 6px #5b4b2d;"]
                    [tr style="background: linear-gradient(to top, #b08d57, #806a38); box-shadow: inset 0 -3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);"]
                        [th colspan="7" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:bold; color:#332b05; text-shadow:0 0 1px #806a35, 0px 0px 2px #b7974d;"]Enmity Generated by JAs/Spells and Gear Influence[/th]
                    [/tr]
                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Action[/th]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Category[/th]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Equipment Set[/th]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Volatile Enmity (VE)
                        [size=10](Base x Total modifier = enmity)[/size]
                        [/th]
                        [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070;"]Cumulative Enmity (CE)
                        [size=10](Base x Total modifier = enmity)[/size]
                        [/th]
                    [/tr]
                    [tr style="background: linear-gradient(to top, #b08d57, #806a38); box-shadow: inset 0 -3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);"]
                        [th colspan="7" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:bold; color:#332b05; text-shadow:0 0 1px #806a35, 0px 0px 2px #b7974d;"]Paladin Main[/th]
                    [/tr]
                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
