            [color=#cea425][b]For Job Abilities (JA):[/b][/color]
            Job Abilities do not require a midcast phase. Their cycle is simpler:

            [div align="center"][table style="border:3px ridge #b08d57; box-shadow: inset 0 0 6px #5b4b2d;"]
                    [tr style="background: linear-gradient(to top, #b08d57, #806a38); box-shadow: inset 0 -3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);"]
