                        [td style="padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;"][b][color=#F7D58B]Idle Phase[/color][/b][/td]
                        [td style="padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070; text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;"]The character is in a neutral state, waiting to activate a Job Ability.[/td]
                    [/tr]

                    [tr style="background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.5);"]
                        [td style="padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;"][b][color=#F7D58B]Execution Phase[/color][/b][/td]
                        [td style="padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070; text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;"]The moment the Job Ability is activated, applying its effect instantly or after a short delay.[/td]
                    [/tr]

