                        [td style="padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;"][b][color=#F7D58B]Return to Idle[/color][/b][/td]
                        [td style="padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070; text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;"]After the ability is used, the character returns to the idle state, ready for the next action.[/td]
                    [/tr]

