                        [td style="text-align:left; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070; vertical-align:top;"][b][u][color=#FFD700]Gear Prioritization Strategy:[/color][/u][/b]  
                            Focus is on maximizing [b][color=#99ff99]HP[/color][/b] to prevent HP loss during gear swaps and maintain consistent survivability.

                            [b][u][color=#FFD700]Priority Breakdown:[/color][/u][/b]
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]13 - Adamantite Armor[/color][/b]: [b][color=#99ff99]HP+182[/color][/b].  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]12 - Chev. Armet +3[/color][/b]: [b][color=#99ff99]HP+145[/color][/b].  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]11 - Chev. Cuisses +3[/color][/b]: [b][color=#99ff99]HP+127[/color][/b].  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]10 - Gelatinous Ring +1[/color][/b]: [b][color=#99ff99]HP+100[/color][/b].  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]9 - Odnowa Earring +1[/color][/b]: [b][color=#99ff99]HP+110[/color][/b].  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]8 - Kgt. Beads +2[/color][/b]: [b][color=#99ff99]HP+60[/color][/b].
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]7 - Chev. Gauntlets +3[/color][/b]: [b][color=#99ff99]HP+64[/color][/b].  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]6 - Chev. Sabatons +3[/color][/b]: [b][color=#99ff99]HP+52[/color][/b].  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]5 - Rudianos's Mantle[/color][/b]: [b][color=#F7D58B]PDT-10%[/color][/b] and [b][color=#F7D58B]VIT+20[/color][/b] (boosts defense).  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]4 - Staunch Tathlum +1[/color][/b]: Moderate [b][color=#F7D58B]DT-3%[/color][/b] and status resistance.  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]3 - Chev. Earring +1[/color][/b]: Adds small [b][color=#F7D58B]DT-4%[/color][/b] and slight [b][color=#99ff99]Cure Potency[/color][/b].  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]2 - Fortified Ring[/color][/b]: [b][color=#F7D58B]MDT-5%[/color][/b] but no [b][color=#99ff99]HP[/color][/b] or [b][color=#F7D58B]DEF[/color][/b].  
                            • [b][color=#F7D58B]1 - Asklepian Belt[/color][/b]: No [b][color=#99ff99]HP[/color][/b], [b][color=#F7D58B]DT[/color][/b], or [b][color=#F7D58B]DEF[/color][/b].
                        [/td]
