                        [td style="text-align:left; padding:5px; border-bottom:1px solid #707070; border-right:1px solid #707070; vertical-align:top; padding:20px;"][b][u][color=#FFD700]Gear Prioritization Strategy:[/color][/u][/b]  
                            Focus is on maximizing [b][color=#99ff99]HP[/color][/b] to prevent HP loss during gear swaps and maintain consistent survivability.

