        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-sird-enmity style="font-size:20px; color: #cea425; text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]SIRD Enmity Set
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
