            [table][tr][td]The [color=#66ccff]SIRD Enmity set[/color] is designed for casting longer spells (e.g. [color=#00ffd0]Geist Wall[/color], [color=#00ffd0]Sheep Song[/color], [color=#00ffd0]Blank Gaze[/color], etc.) without interruption, while remaining tanky and maximizing [color=#ff7f50]Enmity[/color].

                        • [color=#F7D58B]SIRD Cap (102%)[/color]: Ensures uninterrupted spellcasting to secure aggro.  
                        • [color=#F7D58B]PDT & MDT[/color]: Ideally, aim to cap both physical and magical damage reduction.  
                        • [color=#7fe07f]~3000 HP Pool[/color]: Maintains a healthy HP total for survivability.  
                        • [color=#ff7f50]Maximize Enmity[/color]: Boost threat without sacrificing the above stats.

                        By balancing these elements ([color=#F7D58B]SIRD[/color], [color=#F7D58B]Damage Reduction[/color], [color=#7fe07f]HP[/color], and [color=#ff7f50]Enmity[/color]), this set enables consistent casting under heavy pressure and effective threat management.
                    [/td]
                [/tr]
            [/table]
