    "][div align="center" style="margin:15px 0 25px 0; padding:10px;"][img style="width:450px; height:auto;"]https://i.imgur.com/Rd4V1im.png[/img]
            [span style="
            font-size:25px;
            font-family:Garamond, serif;
            font-weight:bold; 
            color:#FFD700; 
            text-transform:uppercase; 
            letter-spacing:1px;
            text-shadow:0 0 1px #5a4614, 1px 1px 2px #7b6119;"]JOB ABILITY SETS Overview[/span][/div]

        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color:#E0E0E0;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-ja-set style="font-size:20px; color: #cea425; text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]JAs Sets
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
                [/div]
            [/div]

            [table][tr][td][color=#66ccff]Job Ability (JA) Sets[/color] are built upon the [color=#66ccff]Full Enmity Set[/color], with specific gear pieces swapped in to enhance each [color=#e5d522]Job Ability[/color]. The foundation focuses on maximizing [color=#ff7f50]Enmity[/color], but using [color=#F7D58B]+3[/color] versions of gear is recommended for the improved [color=#F7D58B]DEF[/color], [color=#F7D58B]VIT[/color], [color=#7fe07f]HP[/color], and [color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] stats. While JA-specific bonuses are identical across NQ, +1, +2, and +3 versions, the extra defensive stats from +3 gear enhance survivability—especially valuable even for the short activation time of JAs.

                        • [color=#F7D58B]Optimized for JAs[/color]: Focuses on maximizing [color=#ff7f50]Enmity[/color] while enhancing the selected Job Ability.  
                        • [color=#F7D58B]+3 Gear Upgrade[/color]: Significantly boosts [color=#F7D58B]DEF[/color], [color=#F7D58B]VIT[/color], [color=#7fe07f]HP[/color], and [color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] for better durability.  
                        • [color=#F7D58B]Flexible Setup[/color]: Swap only the necessary gear pieces to support the JA without sacrificing defense.

                        Below is an example of the [color=#66ccff]Full Enmity Set[/color] followed by a detailed table listing each [color=#e5d522]Job Ability[/color] with the recommended gear to maximize its effect.
                    [/td]
                [/tr]
