    "][div align="center" style="margin:15px 0 25px 0; padding:10px;"][img style="width:450px; height:auto;"]https://i.imgur.com/Rd4V1im.png[/img]
            [span style="
            font-size:25px;
            font-family:Garamond, serif;
            font-weight:bold; 
            color:#FFD700; 
            text-transform:uppercase; 
            letter-spacing:1px;
            text-shadow:0 0 1px #5a4614, 1px 1px 2px #7b6119;"]PHALANX SETS Overview[/span][/div]
        [div align="left"]A [color=#66ccff]Phalanx Set[/color] is designed to enhance the effectiveness of the [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx[/color] spell, which reduces incoming damage by applying a flat damage reduction effect. This type of set focuses on maximizing [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx+[/color] gear while balancing defensive stats to ensure survivability.

            The goal of a [color=#66ccff]Phalanx Set[/color] is to maintain tankiness and durability, making it ideal for mitigating consistent incoming damage in both group and solo situations. By optimizing [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx potency[/color], alongside robust defensive stats like [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color], [color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color], and a solid [color=#7fe07f]HP pool[/color], this setup ensures long-term resilience.

            Below, you will find two variations of the [color=#66ccff]Phalanx Set[/color], tailored to different scenarios to provide both maximum protection and adaptability.
        [/div]

        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color:#E0E0E0;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-phalanx-potency style="font-size:20px; color: #cea425; text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]PHALANX POTENCY
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
                [/div]
            [/div]

            [table][tr][td]The [color=#66ccff]Phalanx Potency Set[/color] is designed to maximize damage reduction by stacking [color=#00ffd0]Phalanx+[/color] gear and achieving [color=#F7D58B]415 Enhancing Magic Skill[/color]. This balance ensures optimal mitigation while maintaining strong defensive stats.

                        This set is primarily used between fights to refresh [color=#00ffd0]Phalanx[/color] with maximum potency. For casting [color=#00ffd0]Phalanx[/color] during combat, it is recommended to switch to the [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx SIRD[/color] set for greater interruption resistance.

                        If losing TP is not a concern, equipping [color=#F7D58B]Sakpata's Sword[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]Priwen[/color] shield will maximize potency, bringing the total [color=#00ffd0]Phalanx[/color] bonus to +69.
                        
                        The build combines high [color=#00ffd0]Phalanx[/color] values with solid defensive stats, achieving [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color], [color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color], and overall [color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] reduction to stay tanky even when not actively engaged in battle.
                    [/td]
                [/tr]
            [/table]
