            [table][tr][td]The [color=#66ccff]Phalanx SIRD Set[/color] is specifically designed for situations where casting [color=#00ffd0]Phalanx[/color] during combat is crucial such as when you've been debuffed or are solo leveling in [color=#F7D58B]Crawler's Nest [S][/color]. This setup ensures maximum [color=#F7D58B]Spell Interruption Rate Down (SIRD)[/color] to maintain uninterrupted casting under pressure, while still providing strong defense and optimal [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx Potency[/color].

                                Whenever possible, prioritize the [color=#66ccff]Phalanx Potency set[/color] between pulls, especially when teamed up with a [color=#F7D58B]Red Mage (RDM)[/color] to extend [color=#00ffd0]Phalanx[/color] duration during events. This proactive approach helps avoid situations where the SIRD set becomes necessary.
                    [/td]
                [/tr]
            [/table]
