    [div style="
    margin:0 auto; 
    background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.85); 
    padding:5px; 
    border-radius:15px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); 
    border:3px ridge #F7D58B;
    "][div align="center" style="margin:15px 0 25px 0; padding:10px;"][img style="width:450px; height:auto;"]https://i.imgur.com/Rd4V1im.png[/img]
            [span style="
            font-size:25px;
            font-family:Garamond, serif;
            font-weight:bold; 
            color:#FFD700; 
            text-transform:uppercase; 
            letter-spacing:1px;
            text-shadow:0 0 1px #5a4614, 1px 1px 2px #7b6119;"]ENHANCING SETS Overview[/span][/div]
        [div align="left"]The [color=#00ffd0]Enlight II[/color] spell enhances both damage and accuracy on melee hits, scaling with [color=#F7D58B]Divine Magic Skill[/color]. The [color=#66ccff]Enlight Set[/color] is designed to maximize the spell's potential while maintaining strong defensive stats to ensure survivability during combat.

        Below is the [color=#66ccff]Enlight II Set[/color], with a detailed description of its purpose and optimal usage.
        [/div]

        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color:#E0E0E0;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-enlight style="font-size:20px; color: #cea425; text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]ENLIGHT II SIRD
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
                [/div]
            [/div]

            [table][tr][td]The [color=#66ccff]Enlight II SIRD Set[/color] is designed to maximize the damage and accuracy bonus from [color=#00ffd0]Enlight II[/color] by stacking high [color=#F7D58B]Divine Magic Skill[/color] and ensuring capped [color=#F7D58B]SIRD (Spell Interruption Rate Down)[/color]. This balance allows for optimal offensive power while maintaining strong defensive stats to safely cast during combat.

                        This set is primarily used during battles to refresh [color=#F7D58B]Enlight II[/color] without risking interruption. For situations where tanking damage is critical, it is recommended to prioritize [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color], [color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color], and [color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] reduction alongside capped [color=#F7D58B]SIRD[/color].

                        The formula for [color=#00ffd0]Enlight II[/color] is:
                        [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](2 × floor((Divine Magic Skill + 400) ÷ 20) + floor((Divine Magic Skill + 400) ÷ 40) + Job Points)[/i][/color][/size]

                        For example, with [color=#F7D58B]569 Divine Magic Skill[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]20 Job Points[/color], the total bonus is:
                        [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](2 × floor((569 + 400) ÷ 20) + floor((569 + 400) ÷ 40) + 20 = +140)[/i][/color][/size]

                        This build effectively balances high [color=#00ffd0]Enlight II[/color] damage and accuracy with solid defensive stats, ensuring survivability with capped [color=#F7D58B]SIRD[/color] and strong [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color]/[color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color]/[color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] reductions during combat.
                    [/td]
                [/tr]
            [/table]
