                • [color=#66ccff]Cure Other Set[/color]: Designed for healing allies, it prioritizes consistent performance without requiring a large HP pool. This set focuses on reliable [color=#F7D58B]Cure Potency[/color] and strong defensive stats to ensure the caster can safely support their team.

