                [/div]
            [/div]

            [table][tr][td]This set is designed to maximize survivability in close combat while maintaining consistent DPS. With high [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color] reduction, excellent accuracy, and optimized TP generation, it perfectly balances defense and offense for demanding battles.

                        [b]Key Highlights:[/b]
                        • [color=#F7D58B]Durability[/color]: Significant reduction in physical and magical damage.
                        • [color=#F7D58B]Offense[/color]: Increased Weaponskill frequency through enhanced TP generation.
                        • [color=#F7D58B]Accuracy[/color]: Reliable hits against high-evasion enemies.

                        [b]Recommended For:[/b]
                        Prolonged engagements where both survivability and offensive performance are crucial.
                    [/td]
                [/tr]
            [/table]
            [div align="center"][div align="center"][table][tr][td vertical-align="middle" style="padding:0px 10px; text-align:center;"][table style="border:3px ridge #b08d57; box-shadow: inset 0 0 6px #5b4b2d;"]
