        [div align="left"][color=#66ccff]Weapon Skill Sets[/color] are tailored configurations designed to maximize the damage output and accuracy of specific weapon skills, ensuring peak performance during combat. These sets focus on optimizing offensive stats such as [color=#F7D58B]STR[/color], [color=#F7D58B]DEX[/color], [color=#F7D58B]Attack[/color], and [color=#F7D58B]Accuracy[/color], while balancing survivability when needed.

            Weapon Skill Sets are typically customized for:
            • The type of weapon skill used (e.g., physical, magical, or hybrid).  
            • The combat situation, balancing raw damage and defensive needs depending on the context.

            By carefully selecting gear to match the mechanics of each weapon skill, these sets ensure both efficiency and effectiveness, allowing the player to adapt to varying combat scenarios with precision.

            Below are examples of [color=#66ccff]Weapon Skill Sets[/color] tailored for specific skill types and situations.
        [/div]

        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
