            [table][tr][td][color=#F7D58B]Savage Blade[/color] is a powerful physical Weapon Skill for Paladins, delivering two hard-hitting strikes with damage scaling based on [color=#F7D58B]50% STR[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]50% MND[/color]. Its potency increases significantly with [color=#F7D58B]TP[/color], reaching its peak damage at 3000 TP with an impressive [color=#F7D58B]fTP[/color] of 13.75.

            When paired with [color=#F7D58B]Burtgang[/color], Savage Blade becomes a reliable tool for dealing high burst damage while maintaining tankiness. It is an essential part of a Paladin's toolkit for both offensive contributions and effective threat generation in combat.

            Below is an optimized set to maximize [color=#F7D58B]Savage Blade's[/color] potential for Paladins using [color=#F7D58B]Burtgang[/color].
