            [table][tr][td][color=#F7D58B]Aeolian Edge[/color] is a magical area-of-effect Weapon Skill that deals [color=#F7D58B]Wind-elemental[/color] damage, scaling with [color=#F7D58B]40% DEX[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]40% INT[/color]. Its potency increases significantly with TP, reaching its peak damage at 3000 TP with an [color=#F7D58B]fTP[/color] of 4.5.

                As a magical Weapon Skill, [color=#F7D58B]Aeolian Edge[/color] benefits from [color=#F7D58B]Magic Attack Bonus (MAB)[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]INT[/color] for maximum damage output. Unlike Cyclone, it requires melee range to be executed, making positioning an important factor when engaging multiple enemies.

                Below is an optimized set to maximize [color=#F7D58B]Aeolian Edge[/color]’s potential, ensuring high magical burst damage while maintaining key survivability stats.
