            [table][tr][td][color=#F7D58B]Sanguine Blade[/color] is a magical Weapon Skill that deals [color=#F7D58B]Dark-elemental[/color] damage and converts a portion of the damage dealt into HP. It scales with [color=#F7D58B]50% MND[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]30% STR[/color], making it a strong option for Paladins in situations requiring sustain.  

                At [color=#F7D58B]3000 TP[/color], [color=#F7D58B] Sanguine Blade[/color] restores [color=#F7D58B]160% of the damage dealt as HP[/color], allowing for significant self-healing when combined with high [color=#F7D58B]Magic Attack Bonus (MAB)[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]INT[/color]. Unlike most [color=#F7D58B]magical Weapon Skills[/color], it does not contribute to Skillchains.  

                The following set is optimized to maximize the damage and healing potential of [color=#F7D58B]Sanguine Blade[/color] while maintaining defensive integrity.  
                    [/td]
                [/tr]
            [/table]
