"][div align="center" style="margin:15px 0 25px 0; padding:10px;"][img style="width:450px; height:auto;"]https://i.imgur.com/Rd4V1im.png[/img]
            [span style="
            font-size:25px;
            font-family:Garamond, serif;
            font-weight:bold; 
            color:#FFD700; 
            text-transform:uppercase; 
            letter-spacing:1px;
            text-shadow:0 0 1px #5a4614, 1px 1px 2px #7b6119;
            "]DOOM SETS Overview[/span][/div]
        [div align="left"][color=#00ffd0]Doom[/color] is one of the most dangerous status effects, causing instant K.O. if not removed in time. It can have a 5- or 10-second countdown, depending on the source, making quick removal crucial for survival.  

            The main ways to remove Doom are:  
            • [color=#F7D58B][b]Cursna[/b][/color] – A spell with variable success rate based on healing magic and gear.  
            • [color=#F7D58B][b]Holy Water[/b][/color] – An item that removes Doom but requires Holy Water+ gear to increase success rate.  

            Because neither method is 100% reliable, preparation is essential. Stacking Doom removal bonuses greatly improves the success rate, making dedicated gear sets crucial in high-end content.
        [/div]

        [div style="
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color:#E0E0E0;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div id=pld-doom style="font-size:20px; color: #cea425; text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]DOOM SET
                    [url=#top style="font-size:14px; color:#2980B9"]▲ Back to top ▲[/url]
                [/div]
            [/div]

            [table][tr][td]The [color=#66ccff][b]Doom Set[/b][/color] is specifically designed to maximize the effectiveness of [color=#F7D58B]Cursna[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]Holy Water[/color] to ensure the highest possible chance of removing [color=#00ffd0]Doom[/color] before it results in K.O.  

                        This set focuses on:  
                        • [color=#F7D58B][b]Cursna+ potency[/b][/color] – Increases the spell’s success rate.  
                        • [color=#F7D58B][b]Holy Water+ bonuses[/b][/color] – Improves item-based removal efficiency.  
                        • [color=#F7D58B][b]Fast gear swaps[/b][/color] – Ensures instant activation when Doom is applied.  

                        By optimizing these elements, the [color=#66ccff][b]Doom Set[/b][/color] provides the best chance to survive encounters where Doom is a major threat.
                    [/td]
                [/tr]
            [/table]
